{
  "text": "The set of case studies was defined with the aim of ensuring that the outputs provided by the developed software match the ones from MCSEnumerator's original implementation. As such, the iAF1260 E. coli GSMM [CITATION_1] was used with different enumeration problems for which the cMCSs were previously determined in the original publication [CITATION_2] . The results from all case studies were accurately replicated and are highlighted in the Table 1.",
  "correct_citation": {
